PROTECTION ACCES
----------------

ip ssh time-out 60
ip ssh logging events
crypto key generate rsa usage-keys label SSH modulus 2048
ip ssh rsa keypair-name SSH
ip ssh version 2  
ip scp server enable
ip access-list standard SSH
permit 100.0.0.1 0.0.0.0
deny   any log
line vty 0 2
access-class SSH in
no ip domain-name

CONFIGURATION GENERALE DE SECURITE
----------------------------------

ip tftp blocksize 8192
no service tcp-small-servers
no service udp-small-servers
no service finger
no service config
no cdp run
no ip http server 
no ip http secure-server
no ip bootp server
no service dhcp 
no snmp-server enable traps 
no snmp-server   
no ip source-route
service tcp-keepalives-in
service tcp-keepalives-out
no service pad
privilege exec level 15 enable
ip arp proxy disable

CONFIGURATION DES LINE
----------------------

line vty 0 2
login local
transport input ssh
transport output ssh
exec-timeout 3 0
loggin synchronous

line cons 0
login local
exec-timeout 3 0
transport preferred none
loggin synchronous

line vty 3 X
login
no exec
transport input none
transport output none

JOURNALISATION DES AUTHENTIFICATIONS
------------------------------------

login on-failure log
login on-success log

PROTECTION CONTRE ATTAQUE FORCE BRUTE
-------------------------------------

login block-for 300 attempts 3 within 120
login delay 2

CONFIGURATION DES LOGS
-----------------------

service timestamps log datetime localtime show-timezone
archive
log config
logging enable
hidekeys
notify syslog
logging size 1000
logging buffered 64000
logging console notifications
logging monitor notifications

